<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">67倍速算法，67与某数（30以内）相乘时，某数是3的几倍，积的末两位数字就是0几，积的首两位数字是末两位数字的2倍。可用公式</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">(n×3)×67=n×200+n</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中某数为n×3（n为任意正整数）。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">67×24=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 67×24</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=8×200+8</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1600+8</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1608</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>